flowchart LR
    A([User Preferences\ngenre · mood · energy · acoustic]) --> B[For each song in catalog\ncompute a match score]
    B --> C{Genre match?}
    C -- Yes --> D[+0.30]
    C -- No --> E[+0.00]
    D --> F{Mood match?}
    E --> F
    F -- Yes --> G[+0.25]
    F -- No --> H[+0.00]
    G --> I[Energy closeness * 0.25]
    H --> I
    I --> J[Acoustic fit * 0.20]
    J --> K[Total score 0.0 to 1.0]
    K --> L[Rank all songs by score]
    L --> M([Top K Recommendations])